I work in a job where it's important to know when the full moon is so you can prepare yourself for the sorts of attitudes and persons you'll be encountering.  Anyone that tries to tell you that the full moon has no effect on things has never worked with the public extensively.  Any ER nurse, doctor or paramedic can tell you they get the weirdest situations and people on the full moon or right around it.  Domestic violence filings and divorce filings are also higher on the full moon.  I like all the info it gives but I don't practice any art that uses it, mostly I wanted it for moon phases and it does that very well.  You can scroll through the dates or spin the moon to the desired phase with your finger.  Only improvement I can suggest is the ability to input a date directly or on a calendar instead of having to hit that arrow key a LOT of times to get back to the 60's etc. etc.  Good product, I'd buy it again, the price is a little high but there is a lot of upkeep and information in it so I can see the price point.
